Package: quallmer.app
Title: Interactive Validation App for Quallmer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Seraphine", "Maerz", , "seraphine.maerz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4289-2098"))
    )
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application for manual coding,
    reviewing LLM-generated annotations, and computing inter-rater reliability
    metrics. Designed to work with the quallmer package for qualitative data
    analysis with large language models.
